is difficult enough.

237
00:12:25,518 --> 00:12:27,788
Getting them to use it
is not predictable.

238
00:12:27,958 --> 00:12:29,581
And how do you target your mark?

239
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,624
Personally,
I'm quite fond of poisons.

240
00:12:31,899 --> 00:12:35,377
