as femine and disarming as possible.

255
00:13:13,376 --> 00:13:15,085
You wore a bikini
made of whipped cream?

256
00:13:16,545 --> 00:13:17,629
I carry a baby.

257
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:21,955
A plastic one, of course.

258
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:24,177
I was born
without a maternal instinct.

259
00:13:25,806 --> 00:13:27,347
The larger question is

260
00:13:27,515 --> 00:13:30,392
what gaps are there in the security
system that we can't account for?

261
00:13:31,122 --> 00:13:33,270
There are always gaps.
You can't account for everything.

262
00:13:33,438 --> 00:13:35,272
We can. We have to.

263
00:13:37,575 --> 00:13:40,067
Let's take a ten-minute break.

264
00:13:40,192 --> 00:13:44,156
I have to have a conference call
with Mr. Bonaventure's advance team.

265
00:13:45,631 --> 00:13:47,238
- Can I talk to you?
- Certainly.

266
00:13:47,363 --> 00:13:48,618
- Excuse me.
- Excuse us.

267
00:13:48,743 --> 00:13:50,018
We'll be right back.

268
00:13:51,601 --> 00:13:53,598
Keep your eyes off my draft, Boyd.

269
00:13:54,529 --> 00:13:55,447
Follow me.

270
00:13:55,572 --> 00:13:57,464
Please tell me
that the trampoline has arrived.

271
00:13:57,589 --> 00:13:59,493
- It's not the trampoline.
