462
00:24:00,889 --> 00:24:03,357
- What kind of suit?
- I believe it was wrongful death,

463
00:24:03,525 --> 00:24:05,026
something in one of our factories.

464
00:24:05,236 --> 00:24:07,588
<i>You still care for her very deeply,
don't you?</i>

465
00:24:07,713 --> 00:24:08,780
<i>That's correct.</i>

466
00:24:09,164 --> 00:24:10,464
It was his wife.

467
00:24:11,534 --> 00:24:14,368
Yes, I believe it was.
As I recall, we settled.

468
00:24:14,665 --> 00:24:16,036
And you don't know his name?

469
00:24:16,478 --> 00:24:19,207
I spend a lot of time in court.
It's the nature of my position.

470
00:24:19,375 --> 00:24:20,291
All right.

471
00:24:20,459 --> 00:24:22,877
O'Hara, let's get on anybody who may
