be able to see him.

602
00:30:35,669 --> 00:30:37,710
And how will you do that?

603
00:30:38,048 --> 00:30:39,587
I will go on first, sir.

604
00:30:41,922 --> 00:30:43,606
What, on? Where?

605
00:30:44,050 --> 00:30:46,927
The podium.
I will stall for as long as it takes,

606
00:30:47,095 --> 00:30:49,096
sensing the crowd, smelling them,

607
00:30:49,265 --> 00:30:51,765
anything out of place,
then the cops and your team,

608
00:30:51,933 --> 00:30:53,976
