and you will follow.

609
00:30:54,862 --> 00:30:56,854
No, that is not acceptable.

610
00:30:59,192 --> 00:31:02,109
- Hand to the head, not working.
- That's why I added sound effects.

611
00:31:03,603 --> 00:31:06,530
Mr. Bonaventure,
I know how this is going to end,

612
00:31:06,698 --> 00:31:09,158
and I am the only one
that can offer you that guarantee.

613
00:31:09,525 --> 00:31:12,741
- Have I been wrong yet?
- The maid, the gardener, the baby.

614
00:31:12,914 --> 00:31:15,094
- Why would you say that?
- I don't know. Symmetry?

615
00:31:15,219 --> 00:31:17,241
Regardless,
I've gotten you this far.

616
00:31:17,366 --> 00:31:20,961
Now what do you value more, your life
or a slight delay in your speech?

617
00:31:29,569 --> 00:31:31,365
Shareholders, board members,

618
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:33,054
members of the press,

619
00:31:33,433 --> 00:31:35,203
attractive businesswomen

