621
00:31:39,954 --> 00:31:43,317
Raise your hand if you vacuum topless
to Carly Simon. I'm kidding.

622
00:31:45,932 --> 00:31:48,268
Welcome.
Welcome, all of you.

623
00:31:48,393 --> 00:31:51,905
My name is Shawn,
and I am the opening act, Jack!

