known we were onto him and got out.

692
00:35:28,174 --> 00:35:29,974
He wasn't listening to us.

693
00:35:32,610 --> 00:35:33,964
He has a microphone.

694
00:35:34,132 --> 00:35:36,049
Who are you talking to?
Who's your partner?

695
00:35:36,217 --> 00:35:38,801
